graph TD
    subgraph Frontend [React + Vite UI]
        UI[Dashboard UI]
        Map[Leaflet/MapLibre Map]
        Chat[Chat Interface]
    end

    subgraph Backend [FastAPI Server]
        API[FastAPI Endpoints]
        Orchestrator[LangChain Agent]
        
        subgraph Tools [Agent Tools]
            T_Spatial[Spatial Query Tool]
            T_RAG[Legal RAG Tool]
            T_Baseline[Baseline Calculator]
        end
    end

    subgraph Data_Layer [Data & Storage]
        PostGIS[(PostGIS DB)]
        Chroma[(ChromaDB Vector Store)]
        Raster[Flood/Land Use GeoTIFFs]
        OSM[OSM Vector Data]
    end

    UI -->|HTTP/WebSocket| API
    API --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator --> T_Spatial
    Orchestrator --> T_RAG
    Orchestrator --> T_Baseline
    
    T_Spatial -->|SQL| PostGIS
    T_Spatial -->|Read| Raster
    T_RAG -->|Query| Chroma
    T_Baseline -->|Read| Raster
    T_Baseline -->|SQL| PostGIS
